          <enum>(1)</enum>
          <text>by striking
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act/s:1302/ss:c/p:2">paragraph (2)</cato:entity-ref>; and</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="H244F2C2A89C9437F847F902238823CEC">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">in <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act/s:1302/ss:c/p:4/sp:A">paragraph (4)(A)</cato:entity-ref>, by striking
			 <quote>paragraphs (1)(B)(i) and (2)(B)(i)</quote> and inserting
			 <quote>
              <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act/s:1302/ss:c/p:1/sp:B/cl:i">paragraph (1)(B)(i)</cato:entity-ref>
            </quote>.</text>
				</paragraph>
      </subsection>
